#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:103
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You can search through the clipboard history by opening it (click on "
#| "&klipper;) and typing your query. The results are updated as you type. In "
#| "case you're wondering how to use the accelerator keys in the &klipper; "
#| "menu, just press &Alt; and the accelerator you want. For example, to "
